PART 4: Software Requirements (Po-Yu)

a. Functional Requirements
  1.Allow user input for ingredients
  2.Back-end filtering of ingredient information 
  3.Hold database of recipes
  4.Connect recipe database to filter for ingredients to search for potential recipes 
  5.Output recipe options for the user 
  
b. Nonfunctional Requirements 
  1.Delete duplicate ingredients
  2.Complete filtering of ingredients and output recipe within 5 seconds 
  3.Provide at least one alternative recipe even if ingredients don't match
  4.Allow organizations that use this system to add their own recipes to database 
  5.Ensure the recipe database complies with Intellectual Property laws 
  
